#define countryAnalytics(filteredData) [[if (filteredData==null){[[global.filteredData=filter(data,x->x[product_idx]=='Saber')]]}
//Grab top countries by sales;
country_grouped = groupByJson(filteredData,country_idx,actual_sales_idx)
top_countries = top(country_grouped, 3)

//Get product name, total sales for product and calculate the percentage of total sales;
prod_name = unique(map(filteredData,x->x[product_idx]))
prod_sales = sum(map(filteredData,x->x[actual_sales_idx]))
pct_of_sales = round(percentage(prod_sales, total_sales),2)

//Calculate pct of sales for product of driving countries and store data in an object;
country_driver_data = map(top_countries, x->(country=x[0], sales=x[1], pct_sales=round(percentage(x[1], prod_sales),2)))

(product=prod_name, product_sales=prod_sales, pct_of_sales=pct_of_sales, drivers=country_driver_data)]]

#define productNarrative(result) [[if (products_desc[0][0]!=asString(result.product)){[[
"The value of sales for [[result.product]] is [[formatCurrency(result.product_sales)]], contributing [[result.pct_of_sales]]% of the total. This was mainly driven by [[map(result.drivers,x->"[[x.country]] [[formatCurrency(x.sales)]] ([[x.pct_sales]]%)")]].

"]]} else {[[topProductNarrative(result)]]}]]

#define topProductNarrative(result) [[
"[[result.product]] performed well accounting for [[result.pct_of_sales]]% of the total sales ([[formatCurrency(result.product_sales)]]). This was mainly driven by [[map(result.drivers,x->"[[x.country]] [[formatCurrency(x.sales)]] ([[x.pct_sales]]%)")]].

"]]

#define numInsightsBySD(values)[[if (values==null){[[global.values=map(groupByJson(data, product_idx, actual_sales_idx), x->x[1])]]}
if (len(values) <= 0) { [[ 0 ]] } else { [[
mean = sum(values) / len(values);
populationStandardDeviation = root(sum(map(values, x->power(abs(x-(sum(values) / len(values))), 2))) / len(values));
len(filter(values, a->(abs(a) >= (abs(mean)+populationStandardDeviation) || (abs(a) <= abs(mean)-populationStandardDeviation))));
]] }]]
